---
title: Spiced Roast Chicken & Bacon Greens with Creamy Leek Sauce & Mash
description: Long after you’ve finished this meal, you’re going to remember the way it was beautifully tied together with the creamiest black garlic sauce. Its unique sweet, savoury and umami-packed flavour works wonderfully with succulent chicken and a side of bacon peppered greens.
